        <para id="id1164566793525">Use the rainfall map on page 1 and your atlas to say which of the following  towns/cities receive the most rain:</para>
        <para id="id8464712">Durban or Bloemfontein  </para>
        <para id="id1164572433004">Port Nolloth or Port Elizabeth  </para>
        <para id="id8554686">Cape Town or De Aar  </para>
        <para id="id4344596">Mossel Bay or Pretoria  </para>
        <para id="id1164568714346"/>
        <para id="id3699290">Read the following statement:</para>
        <figure id="id4107643">
          <media id="id4107643_media" alt="">
            <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics5.png" id="id4107643__onlineimage" height="231" width="633"/>
